description:
Eddie Daniels takes time out to go through the process of selecting a new Clarinet, which can be a daunting process for some. When you're faced with a number of options in selecting your next Clarinet, or woodwind instrument, keep these valuable words of wisdom in mind!

Eddie's playing a Prototype Backun Cocobolo Bb Clarinet with Gold Keys. His Clarinet's sporting a Fatboy Cocobolo Barrel with a Traditional Cocobolo Bell. As for the mouthpiece: it's a MOBA LRT refaced for Eddie. 

To learn more about Backun products and the artists who play them, visit our website and find us on Facebook:

www.backunmusical.com
www.facebook.com/backunmusical

Produced by www.unitednathanproductions.com
